node.text: Everyone, please meet our new family member: Luna! 🌙 We are lucky enough to foster this sweet girl as she recovers from a few procedures. Then we get to officially adopt her! She’s stuck to Carson like glue since day one 💕 Thank you @seattlehumane for all your amazing work🐾 #adoptdontshop #fosterfail
